> samtools/bcftools/bcfutils.c:3:37: fatal error: alloca.h: No such file or directory
> compilation terminated.
> *** [samtools/bcftools/bcfutils.o] Error code 1
>
> Stop in /tmp/Rtmp6FWVKA/R.INSTALL1352730cb1960/Rsamtools/src.
> ERROR: compilation failed for package 'Rsamtools'
> * removing '/usr/local/lib/R/library/Rsamtools'
