This isn't a direct answer to the question, but I recently learned of
this project:

http://www.dexy.it/

Basically, it is a giant set of filters that runs on text-based files
(MANY formats, including org) to produce outputs (MANY formats).
These filters include programming languages (including R) for literate
programming practices.  Dexy might be worth investigating as a general
solution that could be included into Makefiles for vignette
generation.

